OL,5, The UK's biggest business group has    
OL,6, admitted it hired "culturally toxic"   
OL,7, staff and failed to fire people who    
OL,8, sexually harassed female colleagues.   
OL,10,FThe CBI said a failure to act allowed a
OL,11,F"very small minority" of staff to      
OL,12,Fbelieve they could get away with       
OL,13,Fharassment or violence against women.  
OL,15,FThe embattled lobby group said it has  
OL,16,Fnow dismissed a number of people.      
OL,18,FThe CBI was responding to an           
OL,19,Findependent law firm report on         
OL,20,Fmisconduct allegations including rape. 
